snippet.title: Assetto Corsa Competizione Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait is finally over! Assetto Corsa Competizione, the Official GT World Challenge game, is OUT NOW. 

Head out on track and compete against the series’ official drivers, teams and cars, on circuits reproduced using Laserscan technology, offering the highest level of accuracy ever achieved on console.
